{"tid":2114754,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[勸世]  想講下香港好能多人都係亂鳩咁帶口罩","createTime":"2020-07-19T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:06:41.000Z","uid":50878,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe410b9e1e2e947ba9610a4a8e052cb4c540e42","tid":2114754,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"香港由因頭半年既僥倖，令到大部分人以為自己買左口罩就一定安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就無注意好多重要既細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4HgQyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4HgQyZ.jpg&h=86bf0610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.  最常見既拉低口罩 <br />\n其實如果你條頸有菌，d 菌又痴番哂入內側，咁你帶番咪又係食哂d 菌，帶口罩黎裝飾咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SyREOna.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSyREOna.jpg&h=a3bbfbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 用手摸口罩<br />\n又係好常見，用手搞個口罩<br />\n當你口罩外有毒，d 毒又痴哂落你手，你又再摸其他野，<br />\n最鐘意就係摸下個罩再拉低了鼻屎捽眼etc<br />\n儲埋d 毒一次過食哂，yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEEOGJV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEEOGJV.jpg&h=cb9f869b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 放口罩落呢類袋仔，或者褲袋，或者重複用同一個信封<br />\n<br />\n又係果句喇，個罩既毒hi哂落個袋，然後對摺時d毒又hi 番另一面，你又放番個口罩入去，d毒又hi 番入口罩內側一邊，污染哂你將會戴既口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先，以上都係著重於點樣戴罩先保護到自己<br />\n唔好柒碌碌咁明明有戴但又食哂d污糟野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都係少少睇唔過眼9up下，幫唔到幾多<br />\n人人繼續日日迫donki排餐廳 開Party staycation 好撚chill 唔撚驚既話，要爆既最後都要爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如交俾恐懼撚燈死隻毒仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf50a700b76644fc98f45db053bef8ac9a9d477a","tid":2114754,"uid":50878,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">驚閪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eac858f301b46aefc4904a5335898e50ef2cbd","tid":2114754,"uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇聽日確診回落樓主柒到甩碌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1b119b951e6dbe934cb8e99a4f3964fbf2e5fe","tid":2114754,"uid":57578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"警世post 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚多人仲係食飯摺埋口罩放褲袋之後又拎番出黎戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924730dab13f91e13de4937cd710e2dfa1c96f6c","tid":2114754,"uid":50878,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">錯誤示範</span></span>，一失足成千古恨啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 用手摸個罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SorEOzc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSorEOzc.jpg&h=1c614d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 仲要戴住罩kiss<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOJDjFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt